{
  "stem": "22511.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a lovely priest, and I used to tell him everything what's wrong with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What-- I told him the truth, because that was after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I tell him that I have been Jewish and I-- during the war my father put me in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I fighting with myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I always thought that I will be a nun, because I didn't-- only I can see there is a lot of Jewish people alive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I also got, in Argentina, a very big family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother's sister, with kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my daddy wrote everywhere letters that his children are in convent, because he wants to make sure that we'll be back Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he told me this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He used to give me, every Sunday, lollies and nuts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was so nice to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he told me that you don't have to be a nun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You just do what your heart wants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Just one day after the church, I went into the orphan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were a mixture of children-- Jewish and Germans and Ukrainian, Russian-- everyone what didn't have parents went to that place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was a very big panic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The-- the children-- the not Jewish children-- had a fight with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They make the-- not ammunition, just, like bombs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Only that wasn't real bombs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I forgot the name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyway, in that moment, when I came from the church and I saw they start to fight-- no war, and they fight Jewish children-- and my heart start to bleeding.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I saw that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I can't be something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "When they hurt my nation, I was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
